            <div id="story-1">
                <h3>@Localizer["An urgent letter from the director"]</h3>
                <!--<div class="news-subheader mb-4">@Localizer["Homeless women have crucial healthcare, thanks to you"]</div>-->
                <img class="img-fluid story-img" src="~/images/news/issue14/story-1.jpg">
                <figcaption class="figure-caption caption chinese">@Localizer["He has nowhere else to turn. Your gift can give a food parcel and an essential disposable mask."]</figcaption>

                <!--<p class="mb4 clear" style="color: #777777;">@Localizer["By Hanson Ye"]</p>-->
                <p class="mb4 clear">
                    @Localizer["As we write, coronavirus dominates news headlines. It started 500 miles from Shanghai in Wuhan."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["We don't know how long it will last, but today, masks are an urgent need. Homeless people can't find or afford them, but they have to wear them, and nobody can go into a shop or buy food without one. Your help can provide one for those in need."]
                </p>
                <blockquote>
                    @Localizer["I haven't eaten in two days."]<br>
                </blockquote>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["Each mask lasts only a day or two – and although they're now very scarce, we've found a few reliable suppliers who charge slightly higher prices. To comply with the law banning public gatherings, our drop-in center is closed, meaning homeless people have no place to have a hot meal, shower, change of clothes, or laundry."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["Your gift will provide food for people on the streets. Packaged meals and milk cost much more than our communal meals and it takes longer to find the people who need them."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["Homeless people are running out of every means of survival. There are no bottles or other recyclables to be found on the empty streets, and day jobs have disappeared. In the past, people would crew for outdoor events, but all of this is currently out of the question, and only a handful of businesses are open."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["So the situation is getting serious. When we give someone food or a mask, some people tell us, 'I haven't eaten in two days.' Still, we are incredibly grateful for your response to our recent email. Your kind support gives us hope that we can help people through this terrible time, no matter what happens. "]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["Hanson Ye and Jimmy McWhinney"]
                </p>
            </div>
