            <div id="story-2">
                <!--<div class="news-subheader">@Localizer[""]</div>-->
                <h2>@Localizer["Coronavirus hits the homeless"]</h2>
                <div class="news-subheader mb-4">@Localizer["No day labor and no income from recycling means no money, and no food.  "]</div>
                <img class="img-fluid story-img" src="~/images/news/issue14/story-2.jpg">
                <figcaption class="figure-caption caption chinese">@Localizer["Your help can rush food and support to people on the streets."]</figcaption>

                <!--<p class="mb4 clear" style="color: #777777;">@Localizer["By Jimmy McWhinney"]</p>-->
                <p class="mb4 clear">
                    <b>@Localizer["The Story So Far"]</b>
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["Today, many homeless people have nothing to eat but steamed buns with very little nutrition. Many others have no food."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["The streets of Shanghai are empty. There is no recycling to pick up and no day jobs. One person said, 'There is no work, so I don't have money to eat.'"]
                </p>
                <p>
                    <b>@Localizer["Current Street Action"]</b>
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["We are taking your gifts to the streets with parcels of food, milk, and disposable masks. It takes more time and more money. Our typical communal meals are much cheaper, but because the drop in center is closed, they've been banned for now."]
                </p>
                <blockquote>
                    @Localizer["Renewal's drop-in center will reopen the day we can. Until then, we need help to reach people who are stuck outdoors."]<br>
                </blockquote>
                <p>
                    <b>@Localizer["The Human Impact"]</b>
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["People are suffering, and the dirt from the streets is humiliating. Our drop-in center sadly must remain closed for now, giving people no access to a shower, laundry or a clean change of clothes."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["If this crisis continues, we can explore taking fresh clothing onto the streets. At night, there is a chance people might be able to change clothes with dignity."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    <b>@Localizer["What You Can Do"]</b>
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["There's no telling how long the crisis will last, but you can help with a gift for disposable masks, packaged food, and nutritious drinks like milk for people who are stuck outside. The situation is now serious."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localizer["Few people are infected. But the closed businesses and empty streets are hurting the homeless. People who were already on the fringes of society are now pushed to the edge of survival. More and more people are sleeping in parks and in doorways. They really have no other choice."]
                </p>
            </div>
